I would appreciate it if people marked their pull requests for the 1.8 series with the commit hash from the devel &quot;master&quot; that contains the corresponding trunk changeset. This will help me when checking MTT results to see how that change behaved and whether (or not) it is ready to go into 1.8.<br>
